query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT blingOrderId) as total_pedidos_importados,
  COUNT(*) as total_itens_importados,
  MIN(saleDate) as primeira_venda,
  MAX(saleDate) as ultima_venda
FROM sales
WHERE saleDate >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 12 MONTH)
